--- ROOT -- function onReceiveOSC(message, connections) if message[1] == '/device_name' then local device_name = message[2][1].value device_name_control = root:findByName('DEVICE_NAME_CONTROL', true) device_name_control.values['text'] = device_name
local device_name_tab = root:findByName('DEVICE_NAME_TAB', true) device_name_tab.name = device_name end
if message[1] == '/device_address' then local device_address = message[2][1].value device_name_control.values['text'] = device_name_control.values['text'] .. " (" .. device_address .. ")" end end
